Welcome to Poketopia: Unhinged – Saga 1
What begins as a bizarre, comedic ride through a Pokémon world like no other (no humans and they form their own wacky society) quickly reveals deeper layers of satire, chaos, and heart. In this first saga, expect absurd courtrooms, overly dramatic monologues, and a universe where even Pikachu questions his relevance. But beneath the laughs lie characters growing in unexpected ways, friendships that defy logic, and the quiet hum of something much darker forming behind the scenes. If you’ve ever wanted to see what happens when Pokémon drops the main character syndrome and embraces raw, unfiltered weirdness, without humans to order them around as well.... this is your story.

